TRANSPORT
===
==========About project=============
Transport - a small application, which is a schedule of public transport in Minsk.
The application is equipped with the search for the right stop, driving directions, searching vehicles (you can make a choice of transport,
The application uses only ground transportation). This appendix contains the functionality to set the interval time of transport,
which has already left and that will come. As storage schedule using a database SQLite, which works closely application and provides
all the necessary operations. The application is easy to use and has a user-friendly and beautiful interface. The result is a simple, in terms of use,
end-user application. This application is a training, so the database keeps only demos of the application.
====================================
